<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦ - <span class="c1">"الكامل"</span> <span class="c2">(٧/ ٢٦٤١ - ٢٦٤٢)</span> وقال: <span class="c1">"كلُّ رواياته أو عامّتها غير محفوظة"</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧ - <span class="c1">"الإِرشاد"</span> للخَلِيلي <span class="c2">(١/ ٣٥٢ - ٣٥٣)</span> وقال: <span class="c1">"ضعيف جدًّا"</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٨ - <span class="c1">"السنن"</span> للدَّارَقُطْنِيّ <span class="c2">(٢/ ١١)</span> وقال: <span class="c1">"ضعيف"</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
